{"id": "ChIJIxW0AlVL3YARoDsnqfTZ3a4", "rating": 3.1, "userRatingCount": 37, "displayName": {"text": "Devil & Angel Desserts Del Amo", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJIxW0AlVL3YARoDsnqfTZ3a4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GZlFqQk1OMkpOVmxwcE4zRTRSa1JXVmtGQlVVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 2, "text": {"text": "It's interesting coming to the mall and seeing the variety of food and drinks available. The food and drinks at devil & angels look amazing  but they're nothing special that you can't buy anywhere else. A bit overpriced and the only difference is that for some food/drinks fruit is available. The flavoring is a powder and the donuts do look aesthetic. However, I am hesitant to order them after seeing a female worker touching everything, including her phone which is probably dirty and then handling food. Not happy with those standards but you do you.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It's interesting coming to the mall and seeing the variety of food and drinks available. The food and drinks at devil & angels look amazing  but they're nothing special that you can't buy anywhere else. A bit overpriced and the only difference is that for some food/drinks fruit is available. The flavoring is a powder and the donuts do look aesthetic. However, I am hesitant to order them after seeing a female worker touching everything, including her phone which is probably dirty and then handling food. Not happy with those standards but you do you.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Juan Diaz", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115199434266723591698/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKmBqfxwgHmxpx5LR61fUbdSsv0t3V3VgUSO19OFGtZe7joaw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-06-29T22:35:01.502260724Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GZlFqQk1OMkpOVmxwcE4zRTRSa1JXVmtGQlVVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GZlFqQk1OMkpOVmxwcE4zRTRSa1JXVmtGQlVVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80dd4b5502b41523:0xaeddd9f4a9273ba0"}, {"name": "places/ChIJIxW0AlVL3YARoDsnqfTZ3a4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SSWVsbzJZbmxQWkZkU05UQkJhREUxV2tGd1ltYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "I tried 2 things from there- black sugar milk tea and the Dubai covered strawberries. Honestly, the tea was pretty good; however, I totally feel the Dubai covered strawberries were basic. The experience itself was also basic, and it’s a bit pricey. I’m giving it a 4 because I do want to drink more or their drinks to give it an overall rating later on.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I tried 2 things from there- black sugar milk tea and the Dubai covered strawberries. Honestly, the tea was pretty good; however, I totally feel the Dubai covered strawberries were basic. The experience itself was also basic, and it’s a bit pricey. I’m giving it a 4 because I do want to drink more or their drinks to give it an overall rating later on.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Brenna Ray", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113638090694721336933/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIert2ENc6Av0F5trMbLL8jww0w2MJUuFEjcPQrHxtXNd4mvcTG=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-09-27T13:54:23.774502743Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SSWVsbzJZbmxQWkZkU05UQkJhREUxV2tGd1ltYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SSWVsbzJZbmxQWkZkU05UQkJhREUxV2tGd1ltYxAB!2m1!1s0x80dd4b5502b41523:0xaeddd9f4a9273ba0"}, {"name": "places/ChIJIxW0AlVL3YARoDsnqfTZ3a4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxRE5XNVVMVWREWDIxM0xVdENXWE5HUVVoMVJXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "They sell tanghulu here!  Pretty pricey at $7.50 a pop, but it was pretty to look at, fun to try, and the strawberries were huge.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "They sell tanghulu here!  Pretty pricey at $7.50 a pop, but it was pretty to look at, fun to try, and the strawberries were huge.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "I-Lin L", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114118641425706531333/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0g6kEbDzNmY6dOZYU1nXU8yGYkvcUXI3VMrxmwvOYUsgQhMwL=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-02T23:59:21.999807415Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxRE5XNVVMVWREWDIxM0xVdENXWE5HUVVoMVJXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxRE5XNVVMVWREWDIxM0xVdENXWE5HUVVoMVJXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80dd4b5502b41523:0xaeddd9f4a9273ba0"}, {"name": "places/ChIJIxW0AlVL3YARoDsnqfTZ3a4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tFMk5HWjZZbXhmTVV3Mk1XOXFNVE4zVnpKbFoxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "Well the drink was great until my stomach started bothering me. That’s when I found out they didn’t give me what I asked for which is almond milk. Walking around the mall with stomach cramps wondering what happened then get back only for them to tell me well you drunk a good amount of it. Maybe next time. The cashier was awesome but the other lady…..Not good customer service for a drink I paid for. 😔", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Well the drink was great until my stomach started bothering me. That’s when I found out they didn’t give me what I asked for which is almond milk. Walking around the mall with stomach cramps wondering what happened then get back only for them to tell me well you drunk a good amount of it. Maybe next time. The cashier was awesome but the other lady…..Not good customer service for a drink I paid for. 😔", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Roderick Peterson", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114019980085389620984/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ3E7PwGStGp8BDYNBChFrwoQN2vYreqEDXVFYek9ks93KNhA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-16T00:33:35.292997194Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tFMk5HWjZZbXhmTVV3Mk1XOXFNVE4zVnpKbFoxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tFMk5HWjZZbXhmTVV3Mk1XOXFNVE4zVnpKbFoxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80dd4b5502b41523:0xaeddd9f4a9273ba0"}, {"name": "places/ChIJIxW0AlVL3YARoDsnqfTZ3a4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWRmVHRjRTVkJSUlV4dFNXeFlVV3BRWlVwZlJYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "CUSTOMERS BEWARE OF CHIP CULINARY GRADE MATCHA!\nThis place does NOT USE ceremonial-grade matcha. It is very light in color, and the sweetness completely overpowers the flavor. This is culinary-grade matcha  the cheapest kind and it is not meant to be used for drinks. Unfortunately, I didn’t have time to take a photo: after just one sip, I decided to ask for a refund.\nDear business owner, please take a look at what real ceremonial-grade matcha looks like and do not mislead people.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "CUSTOMERS BEWARE OF CHIP CULINARY GRADE MATCHA!\nThis place does NOT USE ceremonial-grade matcha. It is very light in color, and the sweetness completely overpowers the flavor. This is culinary-grade matcha  the cheapest kind and it is not meant to be used for drinks. Unfortunately, I didn’t have time to take a photo: after just one sip, I decided to ask for a refund.\nDear business owner, please take a look at what real ceremonial-grade matcha looks like and do not mislead people.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Svetlana B", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105589758549468054869/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3Mjyxx0Dt4RHYlpAqWw2u7R_-PbuaKo2ySS-sGycWKK0vhsAP=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-02T04:02:31.770030429Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWRmVHRjRTVkJSUlV4dFNXeFlVV3BRWlVwZlJYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWRmVHRjRTVkJSUlV4dFNXeFlVV3BRWlVwZlJYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80dd4b5502b41523:0xaeddd9f4a9273ba0"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJIxW0AlVL3YARoDsnqfTZ3a4/photos/AWCwydi8wDtu6UeEfR_FWo1jJjxDRjCfk_eB9jW73lUgaBPGgFIr1pkvhONrwfgB4C7-Hg1e4dA0R4xhLMFA8oHTIl0Rg6d1liQSsoEGe8MRbf9si3WPCWj_zz-Dn5ebUHORdWzTyZyc-EWr-h361xw3rEKFxAYDm7O1bbP233W9kaoMwVqTfpvovLmDA0zLG-A6GeFQiQsa38Tk3nt2SSwrXUpI5pXNRZhG94ky2_neYSQ4djG96LC0dy2bs6BO6di09MMu2JD8-gFmE7fuv2XWN01wcF_OCsjmOq3OMWB4Qq4R_m0VIa1VQu05X6p5X-lM-jWcPPvq15UYo36rUAIqyC8XUwNhIHZA05qezOVn6qbceDTE6uBpR7S5DpCTGilbeUSByUiUP3_DUuqE8CH_S-D8A3N2Y-VcdognkGQLq1DX5_4spPI5IaR3yl-lyA", "widthPx": 3199, "heightPx": 4800, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Devil & Angel Desserts Del Amo", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/100311686619292888752", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUah3Tdd1Po09jAS9OTa8aDHK1x3XRGNlGxKXUh20noedu5ysU=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIABIhADycKzzjaCXWfCtHUACwHo&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_places.places_api&hl=en-US", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/place//data=!3m4!1e2!3m2!1sCIABIhADycKzzjaCXWfCtHUACwHo!2e10!4m2!3m1!1s0x80dd4b5502b41523:0xaeddd9f4a9273ba0"}, {"name": "places/ChIJIxW0AlVL3YARoDsnqfTZ3a4/photos/AWCwydhg6qyEkzwkOJ53gmBVusam